reviewText: I watched this movie at its theatrical premiere. It is really funny and entertaining.

Excellent and funny!

Fun enough if you don't think too hard. You cant expect a movie with a title like that to take itself seriously. And indeed, it doesnt. There is plenty of unexpected twists that keep the story flowing. There are quite a few good laughs. Altogether, an entertaining film that holds your attention. It is really worth watching.

I think that this movie is not for everyone. I'm hard put to say why I like it - but I do. While I will admit that this isn't exactly Academy Award material, I don't understand the disdain and dislike that some people have shown for it.
One more flick in a silly tradition of B-movies. I love those!

This guilty pleasure movie is not for everyone. Kind of silly, but in places very funny. There is really stuff to enjoy in this film. I haven't seen the 1993 version that some are referring to, I wonder where I can get it.
Great movie, I never knew it existed, but I'm a sucker for this type of movie. It wasn't a blockbuster but I enjoyed the characters and acting greatly.

I love this movie because it reminds me of those cheesy & fun 1970's Italian sex comedies...that actually have no sex. It's silly, fun, it doesn't take itself seriously and it is a true blue B classic! I also liked the original but I think that one was for a 93 audience and the new one is a cult classic for the audience of today. Not for everyone but if you liked Felini's B reel then you'll love this film.
